## Provinces/Cities Collection [/provinces/:id/cities?include=includes&limit=limit]
Cities that are a part of a specific Province can be accessed here.
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Province to perform action with. Has example value.
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier` or `all`

